# Files in this folder that `wrangler dev` must NOT serve as static assets (it points `assets.directory`
# here so it can reach the sibling HTML). Keeps the worker's ASSETS surface to the actual web client:
# the HTML pages, styles.css, and the built dist/*.js — never the TypeScript sources, dev config, or docs.
*.ts
*.jsonc
*.md
.assetsignore
.wrangler
dist/*.map
